{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"033a605d25","title":"肃反你们反了谁？","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（三）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年10月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e982225a2a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"033a605d25"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"393fb9ee2b","name":"太原工学院教师"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fb909b59b2","type":"title","text":"肃反你们反了谁？","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"576f559c94","type":"authors","text":"太原工学院教师","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"b3390ebbf2","type":"paragraph","text":"五人小组严重歪曲党的政策，把好事化为恐怖，133人的名单，使许多无辜的青年人受到了非人的待遇，使人的理想和尊严受到摧残，肃反后逼供的检举材料，封入了毒辣的人事档案袋里，从此便让这些青年人永远投入十八层地狱，永不能翻身。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"58c1099e19","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反你们都反了谁呢？我们所知道的是：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"fc9e920267","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）爱提意见的（不顺风使舵的）；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"958213e775","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）努力工作的（不依靠汇报吃饭的）；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"3e58b6fb74","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）侵犯党员个人虎威的（不拍马的）；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"795a2ee759","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）不服从党员个人命令的（不卑躬屈节的）；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"7a85c01939","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）爱国的华侨和欧美的留学生；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"37c108df86","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）爱国的港澳同胞。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"381f607f0e","type":"paragraph","text":"你们忍心如此，使他们背包袱，政治热情及理想永远消沉，而永远不能冒烟。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"16af685846","type":"paragraph","text":"我们愤怒高呼，把善良人的逼供材料假检举，中伤伪汇报人事室蛮横的肃反材料，在公开大会上烧！烧！烧！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"},{"id":"477d3acc9a","type":"paragraph","text":" 太原工学院一大群教师","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25"}],"page":{"id":"98df865ae6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"033a605d25","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}